This is based on https://github.com/HynDuf/hynduf.github.io.

The source files are mostly the same with the following modified exceptions:

- in _includes/: ads.html, footer.html, head.html, intro-header.html, multilingual-sel.html, nav.html, search.html, sns-links.html
- in _layouts/: default.html, keynote.html, page.html, post.html
- in less/: hux-blog.less
- _config.yaml, about.html, archive.html, index.html

The content files including markdown and images are all new and original to this repository.
